OpenEntry Unified Platform Rebuild
Technologies: PostgreSQL, Redis, Python, DjangoRestFramework, React.js
Hosts: Heroku, AWS

Services in use:
NewRelic for server monitoring and analytics
Sendgrid for transactional email

Services we'd like to try out:
Stormpath for user account management and store access privileges
PhraseApp for text translations
Spreedly for payment gateways
Filepicker for loading in product images from anywhere
Transloadit or Firesize for image resizing
Gioco Pro for some gameification elements in the store builder
Keen.io for Analytics
Adminium for database view interface
Shared Workforce for a human touch regarding user-generated content: text and image quality
Stream for building notification feeds

choose a service for continuous integration when going to production